New Records: Yainer Diaz became the seventh Astros rookie to hit 20 home runs in his first full season.
Key Match Events: Yainer Diaz hit a two-run home run in the fourth inning against the New York Yankees on Saturday at Minute Maid Park.
Post-Match Reflections: Yainer Diaz expressed happiness about achieving his goal of hitting 20 home runs, a milestone set by his parents.
